Class ET_GenericReceiver

java.lang.Object
  android.content.BroadcastReceiver
      com.exacttarget.etpushsdk.ET_GenericReceiver

public class ET_GenericReceiver
extends android.content.BroadcastReceiver

Generic Receiver, useful for catching all kinds of events and intents broadcast by Android.

At the moment, this receiver is used to capture GCM events related to GCM lifecycle (register, unregister, pushes). It inherits from Broadcast Receiver instead of GCMBroadcastReceiver so it can coexist with other GCM handlers, as well as life outside of any specific packages.

This receiver shouldn't require any direct modification.
